    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，GW1负责Protected Resources，GW2负责Protected Services。CTRL是SDP控制器，放在AVD和网关之间做策略控制。三个核心组件都用sdp样式，填充浅蓝色。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CTRL",
